{
  "stem": "7744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I went into the principal's office, and I said to him that I want to go to school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And of course, in those days, particularly in that area, because that's the west of Toronto, there weren't too many Jewish kids, and there weren't too many immigrant kids at the time.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Today it's a different story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- he said to me, well, how much education did you have?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, well, I was three years in Sweden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in Sweden, I did some-- some work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I studied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked me, would I-- he looked at my age, and he said to me, well, I don't really know what to do with you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll put you in grade nine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And grade nine was at least about two years younger than myself, the kids were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He put me in grade nine, and he said he'll take a chance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we developed a rapport as we were talking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know how we were talking, because my English was just a few words here and there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, in Sweden I did learn a little bit of English, where I could between the hands and-- and the expressions I could make myself a little understood.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in grade nine for two weeks or three weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was put into grade 10, because they said that I will work hard enough to-- to succeed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I graduated from York Memorial, I graduated with first class honors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I finished grade-- grade 10, in the assembly hall, they said, we have here a student for the first time promoted to grade 11 [CRYING] with OK, OK, OK, OK in every subject.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no marks.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
